quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,40,"√ëalnde O moo…ìtindiroyta …ìe dendaangal, refti O daalana Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen: \"E ko …ìee …óoo (yim…ìe) rewaynoo on"
  34,41,"∆Åe wi'a: \"Senayee woodanii Ma! Ko An woni gi…óo amen gaanin ma…ì…ìe. Toode ko jinnaaji …óin …ìe rewaynoo, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e ma…ì…ìe, ko …óin (jinnaaji) gom…óini"
  34,42,"Hannde non, yoga mon waawanaa yoga nafa wanaa lorra. Men wi'anoya …ìen too√±u…ìe: \"Mee…óee lepte Yiite nge fennayno…óon fii mun"
  34,43,"Si Aayeeje Amen …ìanngu…óe …óen janngaamma e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'a: \"Oo wonaali, si wanaa gorko faalaa…óo falagol on e ko baabiraa…ìe mon rewayno rewaynoo\". ∆Åe wi'i: \"Ndee (Alqur‚Äôaanaare) wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande\". Yeddu…ìe …ìen wi'ani goonga kan nde ka arunoo e ma…ì…ìe: \"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  34,44,"Men addanaali …ìee, defte …óe …ìe janngata. Men mee…óaali nulude e ma…ì…ìe, jertinoowo ado maa"
  34,45,"Adinoo…ìe …ìe …ìen [kadi] fenniino (nulaa…ìe mun). [Yim…ìe maa …ìen] yottaaki sappa…ìal ko Men okkunoo …ìen kon. ∆Åen fenni Nulaa…ìe Amen …ìen, taskii no lepte Am …óen wa'unoo"
  34,46,"Maaku: \"Anndee ko mi waajorta on, ko (huunde) wootere: \"Ko nde daroranton Alla …ói…óo …ói…óo e gooto gooto, refti miijito…óon. (Anndon) wondii…óo mon on aldaa e jinna: O wonaali, si wanaa jertinoowo on, e ko woni yeeso (mon), e lepte sa…ótu…óe"
  34,47,"Maaku: \"Mi lamndaaki on njo…ìdi, …óum ko fii mon. Njo…ìdi am ndin wonaali, si wanaa ka Alla. Kanko Ko O Seedii…óo e kala huunde"
  34,48,"Maaku: \"Pellet, Joomi am ko werlortoo…óo [meere nden, hujjaaji] goonga kan, timmin…óo anndugol wirnii…ói"
